2026-05-02T22:13:31.5828382Z 13    <!--
2026-05-02T22:13:31.5840000Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-02T22:13:31.5840873Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-02T22:13:31.5842081Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-02T22:13:31.5842966Z 17        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-02T22:13:31.5843860Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
2026-05-02T22:13:31.5844579Z 19        we only request it when the toggle is on.
2026-05-02T22:13:31.5845096Z 20    -->
2026-05-02T22:13:31.5845728Z 21    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.USE_FULL_SCREEN_INTENT" />
