2026-05-02T22:13:31.5847754Z 21-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:16:22-78
2026-05-02T22:13:31.5848667Z 22    <!--
2026-05-02T22:13:31.5849216Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-02T22:13:31.5849902Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-02T22:13:31.5850559Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-02T22:13:31.5851372Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-02T22:13:31.5852174Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-02T22:13:31.5852966Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-02T22:13:31.5853769Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-02T22:13:31.5854568Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-02T22:13:31.5855355Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-02T22:13:31.5856084Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-02T22:13:31.5856654Z 33    -->
2026-05-02T22:13:31.5857246Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
